g.ns0:text: \\noindent input flow $\\phi$ on directed network G=(V,E,s,t,c):\\\\\n\\indent initialize $S={s}$\\\\\n\\indent while there is an arc $xy \\in E$ such that either\\\\\n\\indent \\indent (a) $x \\in S$ $y \\notin S$ and $\\phi(xy) < c(xy)$ or\\\\\n\\indent \\indent (b) $y \\in S$ $x \\notin S$ and $\\phi(xy)>0$\\\\\n\\indent \\indent if (a) add $y$ to $S$ if $(b)$ add $x$ to $S$\\\\\n\\indent if $t \\in S$ then $S$ has an augmenting path\\\\\n\\indent \\indent augment $\\phi$ and call self with $\\phi$\\\\\n\\indent if $t \\notin S$ then $(S, V \\setminus S)$ is a min cut and $\\phi$ a max flow\\\\\noutput $\\phi$
